snippet.title: Alohomora - The True Emperor (Lyrical) | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe üëâ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Alohomora - The True Emperor'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. 

Song Credits:
Name: Alohomora - The True Emperor
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By: B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer: Aniruddha Sastry
Lyrics: Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer: Santhu Master
Keyboard: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Raja Ravi Varma
Rhythm: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Kalyan Chakravarthy
Electric Guitars: Sam Sundar, Viyaan Veer
Chorus: ASR Choir Team Supreeth Phalguna, Abhishek MR, Hrushikesh BR, ASR
Choir Conducted & Recorded By: Aniruddha Sastry
Song Mixed & Masterd By: Pukhraj Sonkar
Assistant Engineer: Dipesh Dhruw Inhouse Studio Mumbai
Music Production: C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, ABBS Studios Bangalore

Production Team:
Produced By : J Jayamma & Saregama
Banner : Shri Jai Matha Combines
Directed By : Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanthraj S S
Costumes : Chethan & Thashwini Veer
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth

Technical Team:
Director Of Photography : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Editor : Harish Komme
Song Editor : Sohan Galgali
Online Editor : Naveen Shetty
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Vivek Anand
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
CG & VFX : Trayom Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Subtitle : Ashwin Sriram
Publicity Design : Kaani Studio
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PR & Marketing : Purvi Kulkarni
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh
Digital PR : Pavan Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Pallavi:
Alohomora The True Emperor
Doubtey Beda Saitaanu Devare..
Astalavista Helade Iro
Bandhanadale Takaraaru Tondare

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will
You‚Äôll Find Evil
Brace Yourself And See
Who‚Äôs The Real Devil ‚Ä¶.
Cho - Ratatatata
Cho - All Rise For The Devil ‚Ä¶.

Charana:
Surya Chandra Milanaane Grahana
Sihi Maatina Hinde Kahi Marma Mouna

Srishti Huttu Drishteene Saavu
Baduku Bella Annode Bevu

Mukhaavadada Badukannu Bodhisuvane Katuka
Usiraatake Koneyelli Husi Iruvaa Tanaka

Janana Marana Naduve Vyasana Payana
Parama Satya Onde Jagada Nidhana

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will
You‚Äôll Find Evil
Brace Yourself And See
Who‚Äôs The Real Devil ‚Ä¶.

Cho - Ratatatata


Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

Presenting the official trailer of ek≈ç, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ek≈ç marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence ‚Äî exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Yaad Jo Aati Hai,

Bas Teri Kahani Hai,

Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Woh Baatein
Woh Chhahat Ki Rasmein

Jaane Tamannah Kya Yeh Sacch
Hai Bas Itna Kehe De
Tut Jaaye Na Lamha Aitbaar Ka
De Koi Sila Mere Intezaar Ka
Chaaha Hai Tujhko Chahungi Har Dam
Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Hu Teri
Jo Chaahe Kasam Le Le
Mujhko Humraahi
Tu Apne Gam De De

Dard Judai Ka Sehena

Manzile Meri
Mere Sath Jayengi
Mushkile Meri

#VARANASI to the World - Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | Prithviraj | SS Rajamouli

Here is our reaction to the teaser of VARANASI, starring Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra Jonas, and Prithviraj Sukumaran. Presented by SS Rajamouli, the film introduces Mahesh Babu as Rudhra ‚Äî a globe-trotting force rising from the spiritual heart of India. Directed by SS Rajamouli, with music by M.M. Keeravaani, Varanasi is produced by KL Narayana and SS Karthikeya under Sri Durga Arts and Showing Business. Watch our full breakdown as we discuss the world-building, performance, visuals, and what this glimpse reveals about the scale and storytelling of this epic.

Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. snippet.title: New Update - Town Hall 18 in Clash of Clans!
snippet.description:
TH18 Update Sneak Peek for Clash of Clans! Judo Sloth Gaming shares Town Hall 18 Gameplay including Guardians, as well as information on New Troop and Defense Levels coming in the update. The Town Hall will now have the Longshot or Smasher Guardians as the defense. The New Troop is the Meteor Golem, which made an appears previously as an event troop. This is only Sneak Peek 1 for the CoC November Update so be sure to subscribe for more Town Hall 18 content. The exact TH18 release date is not confirmed yet but it is typically shortly after sneak peeks and normally when Hammer Jam ends, which is only a few days away. Clash On!

Suggested Videos:
100 Days F2P to Unlock the 6th Builder: https://youtu.be/61wfiVRIPhY
Beating Every Goblin Map WITHOUT Troops: https://youtu.be/2jAkp-m6CNw

snippet.title: Indonesia Coach bus driving | Euro bus simulator 2025 Android gameplay #game 1
snippet.description:
Indonesian Bus Simulator Game with the latest features 

This game of Indonesia Bus Simulator will make you feel like a real bus driver when you play it. Coupled with the quality of the graphics which are very pleasing to the eye, the combination of sharp and realistic colors will make you more comfortable to playing this game. The route your bus takes to get to the destination city is almost exactly the same as the original road. Supported by realistic traffic conditions and you can choose the crowd level, this game never gets boring to keep playing!

And in this game, you can choose the steering wheel mode according to your wishes! There is a right-left button mode, there is a gadget shake model, and there is also a steering wheel mode like the original! This game is also equipped with various cool features. Equipped with an automatic open-close door button, 3D horn sound, turn signal lights, hazard lights, wipers, hand brakes, high beam lights and several camera modes. You also don't need to worry about getting lost when heading to your destination city because there is a map feature to guide you!

In this game you can also measure your success in playing this game by the amount of money you can collect. You can earn this money from your work delivering passengers to destination cities. But you don't have to spend the money you have earned just to buy fuel, because in this game you don't need to refill your bus with fuel. From the money you collect, you can buy another bus. In total there are 2 types of buses that you can use, and both are double cabin buses or double-decker buses. Of course, this is a very exciting mission to undertake in order to have the bus of your dreams!

So what are you waiting for! There is no reason for you to not downloaded this game immediately. Hurry up and drive your bus, and go to your destination city so you can have lots of money. And feel the real excitement by becoming a real bus driver!
